1. Download and extract zip file on Desktop.
2. Download and run Docker on Pc.
3. Open Command Line and write the following command to run it : 
    > docker run redis
4. open another cmd window and write :
    > cd Desktop/visits
    > docker-compose up
4. Open Browser and go to localhost:4001
5. Output will be displayed.(everytime you refresh the page, Number of page visits will be increased)
